welcome_message_title: Welcome to Leeds and the Thousand Islands
welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Leeds and the Thousand Islands, Canada! Experience the charm of our beautiful city known for its stunning landscapes and rich history. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that it has to offer."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Brockville Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
